**Proxy**
Full name: "ETH>IP>TCP>HTTP>PROXY"
Description: HTTP/HTTPS proxy server
Example: "Start an HTTP proxy on port 8080"
Startup parameters:
  • certificate_mode (optional) - Certificate mode: 'generate' (MITM with generated cert), 'none' (pass-through, no MITM)
    Example: "generate"
  • cert_path (optional) - Path to certificate file (only if certificate_mode is 'load_from_file')
    Example: "/path/to/cert.pem"
  • key_path (optional) - Path to private key file (only if certificate_mode is 'load_from_file')
    Example: "/path/to/key.pem"
  • request_filter_mode (optional) - Request filter mode: 'all' (intercept everything), 'match_only' (only if filters match), 'none' (pass through)
    Example: "match_only"
  • response_filter_mode (optional) - Response filter mode: 'all', 'match_only', or 'none'
    Example: "all"
  • https_connection_filter_mode (optional) - HTTPS connection filter mode (pass-through only): 'all', 'match_only', or 'none'
    Example: "match_only"

